delete_gui_object(25.10)                              delete_gui_object(25.10)

Name
       delete_gui_object - Deletes specified or selected GUI objects

Syntax
       delete_gui_object

       [-help]

       [-shape | -text | -marker | -all | -selected ]

       Deletes specified or selected GUI objects.

Parameters
       -help  Prints  out the command usage. For a detailed description of the
              command, use the man command:

               man delete_gui_object

       -all   Deletes all GUI objects.

       -marker
              Deletes GUI markers.

       -selected
              Deletes selected GUI objects.

       -shape Deletes GUI shapes.

       -text  Deletes GUI text.

Related Information
              * add_gui_marker

              * add_gui_shape

              * add_gui_text

